E5%9C%8B%E8%A3%BD%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmartinoei.com%2Farticle%2F27939%2F%25E5%2585%258B%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E9%25BB%259E%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E5%2592%2581%25E9%25A9%259A%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25A3%25BD%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E5%2599%25A8&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY%2FTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=9cdcb165\" target=\"_blank\">https://martinoei.com/article/27939/%E5%85%8B%E8%AD%A6-%E9%BB%9E%E8%A7%A3%E5%92%81%E9%A9%9A%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%A3%BD%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8</a><br />\n<br />\n泰國2008年曼谷要鎮壓反政府示威，出動由中國買返嚟嘅催淚彈，結果係搞出人命，事後發現係因為中國製催淚彈落得太多炸藥，結果勁到可以炸死人，你諗吓啲差佬用果陣唔會驚，呢啲質量失控嘅情況，唔係玩緊《回魂夜》嘅俄羅斯練膽大法又係乜？當然，既然會有催淚彈火藥落得太多炸死人，就會有火藥無落過，或者彈殻偷工減料，結果未掟出去已經自己吸晒。呢啲荒謬事情太多，就唔會有作戰能力，所以今時今日 克警 仲要問英國、美國買武器理由亦喺呢度，因為中國武器啲品質係十分之成疑。當然，呢個亦係共產國家特色。"},{"pid":"e7d03e119bc606c05efa4b83cecaac05488f336e","tid":1507460,"uid":68483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:35:39.000Z","msg":"買中國貨就好喇，遲早有一日tk"},{"pid":"8dc91f4c60cf2bd6eccdabf89e2f16a22b5c3f9e","tid":1507460,"uid":173002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:39:39.000Z","msg":"前線要小心，強國產會比進口貨熱好多，直接處理一定要戴隔熱手套。"},{"pid":"8a6ec7c058db6e63aae0c77d8adc49e8ea1f1154","tid":1507460,"uid":44646,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6766498803fd833da1312e890f8903848f8f044a","tid":1507460,"uid":14918,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:18:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:41:01.000Z","msg":"唔使發夢，早幾日犬方買左500套大家產犬用裝甲<br />\n見曬報"},{"pid":"b8b1567f0d8ccf1b80e4c2081a241f4d79696928","tid":1507460,"uid":139667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5354c629094eda5863a562aaa845bef05ef2a26e","tid":1507460,"uid":169665,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:18:57.000Z","msg":"大陸製一定含有其他有毒物質 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07